               <msContents>
                  <summary>Papyrus business letter from Egypt. Acknowledges the receipt of the addressee's instructions and announces the imminent inception of work relating to the plots of land (likely vineyards or gardens) of a monastery named after the martyr Victor</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Actual dimensions of item are 7.7 x 16.7 cm</note>
                     <note type="general">7 lines</note>
                     <note type="general">Written across the fibers on the recto; written along the fibers on the verso</note>
                     <note type="general">Upper margin of 1.5 cm</note>
                     <note type="general">P.Duk.inv. 497 was formerly P.Miss. 63</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="grc">In Greek</textLang>
                  </msItem>
